title: Healthy Ep. 6 - Playing it safe? This is for you. {with Mike Todd}
description:
Are you missing out what God has for you because they're playing it safe? Get ready. This episode is for you, no matter where you are right now in your journey.

Find Mike's book 'Crazy Faith' here: https://www.amazon.com/Crazy-Faith-Only-Until-Happens/dp/B08ZRLYYYC

Thanks, Stamps.com! No long-term commitments or contracts. Just go to Stamps.com, click on the Microphone at the TOP of the homepage and type in MADEFORTHIS for a special offer that includes a 4-week trial PLUS free postage and a digital scale.
